data.description: Just in time for the holidays. This ''Beautiful Executive Home'' is perfect for those families that love big family gatherings. Home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, an open floor concept with lots of natural lighting. Open living room /formal dining area, formal living room or could be used as an office. Foyer opens into the formal dining room living room with a beautiful stone hearth/cozy electric fireplace, double trey ceilings, eat in kitchen, breakfast bar, lots of cabinets and counter space, split floor plan with a beautiful, oversized master ensuite with sitting area. Guest bedroom, two of the other bedrooms have the jack and jill bathroom connected. Convenient to shopping, entertainment, restaurants, airport, military bases. Seller will give 5,000 flooring allowance for carpet replacement & pay 3,000 in closing cost with acceptable offer.  The VA loan can be assumed interest rate of 3.25
